snippet.title: Retro Gadgets - Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
📟Retro Gadgets Early Access is OUT NOW! 📟
Steam: https://s.team/a/1730260/
Discord: https://discord.gg/np6FUDjt9E

Retro Gadgets is a gadget creation station where you invent, build, solder, code and customise your own electrifying gadgets then share them with the world.

Song by:
Mygg (Jonas Sarvik)
Bossman (Rob Cowell)

The Gadgets showcased in this video were made by these amazing individuals:
